reviewText: i love dance acadmy so much. Although its for the younger kids but i really enjoy it myself I purhased the dvd from Amazon.
Love this TV show and glad I can get the DVDs and not trust the streaming gods to make available to me.
This oringonally aired on the CW, then went to neflix, then to dvd. But was a great teen drama show. I bought this to go with my other teen series.

Absolutely wonderful series.  Lead dancer, Tara, is exquisite, and other dancers are outstanding.  Hard to believe there is this much talent in Australia and grateful I was flipping through channels on TV and saw this show accidentally one Saturday so bought the collection.  Only thing NOT believable is the lack of adults in the dorms at nighttime and the fact that most of the kids actually get along with each other.
